Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper focuses on generating realistic images from text descriptions, which is a core problem in computer vision. 
2. cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper also involves natural language processing, as it uses dialogue to improve the text-to-image generation. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a model that uses deep learning techniques to generate images from text and dialogue. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper involves the use of AI techniques to generate images from text and dialogue. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper involves retrieving information from text and using it to generate images, which falls under the scope of information retrieval.
